metadata.name: Proof Of Existence - The Sidelines
metadata.description: For most of 2022, I have spent most of my time observing, learning, and trying to find my place in the world of Web3. Like many, I have struggled with fear and doubt, which has held me back from taking action. However, I am ready to make my first contribution to this space with a 1/1 NFT series called Proof of Existence. Each drop will serve as a stamp on the blockchain, marking the beginning of this journey. Iâ€™m jumping up from the sidelines to embrace the unknown, taking a leap of faith and leaving my mark one photo at a time.
